ge-samples-brazil&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhathVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=24db99cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/world/americas/article/3091757/earlier-signs-coronavirus-sewage-samples-brazil</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社報道去年3月西班牙污水樣本發現新冠病毒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-spain-science/coronavirus-traces-found-in-march-2019-sewage-sample-spanish-study-shows-idUSKBN23X2HQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-health-coronavirus-spain-science%2Fcoronavirus-traces-found-in-march-2019-sewage-sample-spanish-study-shows-idUSKBN23X2HQ&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhathVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=21475bdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-health-coronavirus-spain-science%2Fcoronavirus-traces-found-in-march-2019-sewage-sample-spanish-study-shows-idUSKBN23X2HQ&h=4201d4fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-spain-science/coronavirus-traces-found-in-march-2019-sewage-sample-spanish-study-shows-idUSKBN23X2HQ</a><br />\n<br />\nCGTN訪問美國貝爾維爾市市長米高&middot;梅勒姆報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cgtn.com/news/2020-05-07/Belleville-mayor-believes-he-others-contracted-COVID-19-last-November-QijASNqQ1O/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cgtn.com%2Fnews%2F2020-05-07%2FBelleville-mayor-believes-he-others-contracted-COVID-19-last-November-QijASNqQ1O%2Findex.html&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhathVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=7e97c41a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cgtn.com/news/2020-05-07/Belleville-mayor-believes-he-others-contracted-COVID-19-last-November-QijASNqQ1O/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國貝爾維爾市市長米高&middot;梅勒姆Twitter帖文<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/michaelmelham/status/1257695516416188418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmichaelmelham%2Fstatus%2F1257695516416188418&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhathVENBC9V